Usage: registerTrigger [-help] [{-pre  | -post } <commandName> <procName>]

-help             # Prints out the command usage
<commandName>     # Specifies command name (string, required)
<procName>        # Specifies proc name (string, required)
-post             # Specifies -post option (bool, required)
-pre              # Specifies -pre option (bool, required)